Definition: law) a security entered into before a court with a condition to perform some act required by law
Example: on failure to perform that act a sum is forfeited
Synonyms: recognisance, security, noun, group, law, c, a, entered, into, before, court, with, condition, to, perform, some, act, required, by, on, failure, that, sum, is, forfeited
Category: noun.possession
